                     <interp inst="t18111030-90-person768" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am in the workhouse. I was sent to the cupboard with a wheel, I found the pewter bottoms, I looked at them and put them in again, I went and informed my mistress.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. I am sure they are mine.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I hope master will recommend me to mercy.</p>
